      "text": "We seem to be making progress, [player name]. Keep it up.",
      "placeholders": [
        "[player name]"
      ]
    },
    "2acdac10c155ba0f42f97b39f80cd61ca1f51200d6b74b0dba00246f20f3ab99": {
      "text": "I'm already there, [player name].",
      "placeholders": [
        "[player name]"
      ]
    },
    "a4bea10b7f1278cfa90fcff0d36e74468a7f7d9ef32ad717f673f431be37a1b3": {
      "text": "Nice work, [player name]! I think you did it!",
      "placeholders": [
        "[player name]"
      ]
    },
    "06688b1fe95ff593b2c4a964a1f99f9872b3812922104d669807cdca4249cf24": {
      "text": "When you're ready, [player name].",
      "placeholders": [
        "[player name]"
      ]
    },
    "536957c58f2ec273603e1ece4e9b9181aa9c8b95405e4239e2e7720f1bcf0eb7": {
      "text": "They can't be too far ahead now. Let's find them, [player name].",
      "placeholders": [
        "[player name]"
      ]
    },
    "9dd53697ff99d1141967cd0d2e2279b826ca38943c9349b3dd1fb905beb484ee": {
      "text": "Are you coming, [player name]?",
      "placeholders": [
        "[player name]"
      ]
    },
    "0d782c76e79d3af8e6584720863e90c22539164bca5eed34a251cc37433d3b68": {
      "text": "Ah, there you are, [player name].",
      "placeholders": [
        "[player name]"
      ]
    },
    "1099b6b8e90c6cef8f83526f28ca67aa737aa811aae037d4acedee23c59476dd": {
      "text": "Nilsal, [player name]. As I was saying, it feels only right for me to show my thanks to you by giving you a little something.",
      "placeholders": [
        "[player name]"
      ]
    },
    "69bd9dc882a9b4f463e2f77ea24fc4b1584e9d27d3179c9171b889c604a20177": {
      "text": "Nilsal, [player name].",
      "placeholders": [
        "[player name]"
      ]
    },
    "54aad356be0f4334f9e4f25b345ef3aab1422a8f77f76a8c5264a458c7eb5224": {
      "text": "One of the only people left that I can trust. They'll fill you in on the details of how you'll infiltrate the Emissaries. Good luck, [player name]. May the sun light your way.",
      "placeholders": [
        "[player name]"
      ]
    },
    "22df0f2b98cde84e872a3b5f18c20899fceac3940f70d8f3cbe08639d07a59a3": {
      "text": "Nilsal, [player name]. You should head on over to the pub in Quetzacalli Gorge. Remember, you'll need to rent the basement room. My contact will meet you there.",
      "placeholders": [
        "[player name]"
      ]
    },
    "f0220d516a3f3857332d34deb56cd91f906a657384faa17af4ddc0b4ab48c324": {
      "text": "We do not need to do this dance, [player name]. I understand that where you come from, there is a certain art to holding a conversation. We do not bother with that here. You may be direct.",
      "placeholders": [
        "[player name]"
      ]
    },
    "561a7c419cd103d057d0ea82e9cc6162612580a2794392976daeb66620b8dd68": {
      "text": "Nilsal, [player name]. Any luck with that shopkeeper?",
      "placeholders": [
        "[player name]"
      ]
    },
    "62ec5fc3ad2ca3aa96a2d2d46ae17310af394050f67f46b89e08a4918abe8a4d": {
      "text": "Great work there, [player name]. I wonder what our next trial will be.",
      "placeholders": [
        "[player name]"
      ]
    },
    "167a51ee065f05198f37e323ee20da35f801f57a8320168b1f6fec25bd38a254": {
      "text": "How's it going, [player name]?",
      "placeholders": [
        "[player name]"
      ]
    },
    "068c3b951a37e0d6692d8404ebb6637a81dca5e039a195efcb64a005b78f3a23": {
      "text": "Great work, [player name]. On to the final trial!",
      "placeholders": [
        "[player name]"
      ]
    },
    "54f063fdf39f5c8ded6eb470691f1da402e78d11281acf403d2c4a2cab6502c3": {
      "text": "Well, you heard the man, [player name]. Shall we dance?",
      "placeholders": [
        "[player name]"
      ]
    },
    "20572fef2db16496920bc18d04e17c8e3dd72ddbbef30bfcfc7fab8a7193332a": {
      "text": "Great work opening the door, [player name]. Time to see what awaits us on the other side.",
      "placeholders": [
        "[player name]"
      ]
    },
    "5bdc7d4858425050453c1e6f7837b6f8590a9a78be7c1136293930230a23098d": {
      "text": "Yes, very fun stuff. All a bit of a convoluted mess as well! I'll be sure to tell you all about it at some point. For now though, [player name], meet Servius. Servius, meet [player name].",
      "placeholders": [
        "[player name]",
        "[player name]"
      ]
    },
    "7e936cdfe21f3cf0e70e08b12bb4c1945a185aa3b2b9e85c0c4765644f8e9459": {
      "text": "Right you are, [player name]! In fact, it limits them to just the members of our little delegation. In other words, myself, Servius, the Tullus twins and our retinue of knights.",
      "placeholders": [
        "[player name]"
      ]
    },
    "ef6064aaa6e1b5cfb2998c8b6db4b4c71997421ed7eeb827cd4b809870ac58d4": {
      "text": "[player name], since Servius here seems keen on letting this killer have another go, you'll need to investigate the knights on your own.",
      "placeholders": [
        "[player name]"
      ]
    },
    "fdd5003614bf5a20dd73fc076a3e42951f41599f90a9b917922355e34f99c7af": {
      "text": "[player name], head to the palace and find the Tullus twins. They'll know where you can find those knights.",
      "placeholders": [
        "[player name]"
      ]
    },
    "3fa7abde8ece52ff0791d9d40671529203a84a0bc4d5ed03557e29c1acbd52ca": {
      "text": "Nilsal, [player name]. How goes your investigation?",
      "placeholders": [
        "[player name]"
      ]
    },
    "7bfa7f24704acd423cfd15d2f71169f50209f9738d0a8b22ca598cc2d6aae2df": {
      "text": "Nilsal, [player name]. Welcome to the Teomat.",
      "placeholders": [
        "[player name]"
      ]
    },
    "17a8df765e1157cc37e7ed024a89806fba7c16ae81a1a926d5ed6ec9b25f9ce3": {
      "text": "Yes, very true, but [player name] also has valid concerns. We need to be careful of assumptions, but it seems it would be wise for us to keep an eye on the two of them from now on.",
      "placeholders": [
        "[player name]"
      ]
    },
    "93e6c64b613cb5764e5c129bef05c9bd2c7884bb8f82351d010b658b9046f6c0": {
      "text": "Now, [player name], did your investigation uncover anything else?",
      "placeholders": [
        "[player name]"
      ]
    },
    "d84c0798123c061da00dd46ab2946718a531b7034cd60cd419da96bd56a79e4f": {
      "text": "[player name]! I need you outside, now! We have a little bit of an issue!",
      "placeholders": [
        "[player name]"
      ]
    },
    "fadd279f774aac2f14b2c2296e0a1d6829867a21e02e1e62b176547d58d9a3b7": {
      "text": "I'll be here, [player name].",
      "placeholders": [
        "[player name]"
      ]
    }
  }
}